title: Onething Live Discography 2011-2014 (4 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
ONETHING LIVE DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 4 releases...

 * 2011 - Before His Eyes
 * 2012 - Magnificent Obsession
 * 2013 - You Satisfy My Soul
 * 2014 - Sing Your Praises

Onething Live is an annual Christian conference put on by the International House of Prayer every December at the Bartle Hall Convention Center in Kansas City MO.

Be Blessed,
TorrentTracts - December 2015
